title: A Sheltered Boy: My Name Is Gohan
description: Start of the "Vegeta Saga". It has been five years since the defeat of Piccolo, and Goku and Chi Chi have settled down at Goku's old home in the forest. They now have a son named Gohan, named after Goku's grandfather. One day Goku is supposed to meet his old friends for a reunion at Roshi's house, but before he leaves he must find Gohan, who is lost in the forest. Meanwhile, a mysterious Saiyan warrior lands on Earth and searches for someone named Kakarot. Instead, he finds Piccolo, who is still training to defeat Goku.

title: History's Strongest Warrior Is Goku's Older Brother
description: Everyone arrives at Roshi's house for the reunion, but the Saiyan warrior crashes the party. He reveals himself to be Raditz, Goku's older brother, and he explains the history of the Saiyan race. He also reveals that Kakarot is the birth name of Goku, also a Saiyan, who was sent to Earth as an infant to extinguish all life.

title: This Is It! The World's Strongest Pair
description: Hoping to force Goku into following his orders, Raditz abducts Gohan. While Goku and the others decide what to do next, Piccolo shows up. Realizing that Raditz is too powerful for either fighter to defeat alone, Goku and Piccolo forge an alliance and confront him.

title: Piccolo's Secret Ace! Gohan the Crybaby
description: Goku and Piccolo fight Raditz. While Goku fends Raditz off, Piccolo attempts to gather enough energy to use his newest attack.

title: The Death of Son Goku
description: In a rage, Gohan breaks free from his prison and attacks Raditz. Goku distracts Raditz in an attempt to save Gohan, and Piccolo charges his Special Beam Cannon for one final attack. Meanwhile, two other Saiyans hear Piccolo speak of the dragon balls through Raditz's scouter and decide to come to Earth.

title: The King Is Shocked: Fighting Is His Netherworld?
description: Goku's friends form a plan to bring him back to life with the dragon balls, and Piccolo takes Gohan away to train in preparation for the arrival of the two Saiyans. Meanwhile, Kami meets Goku in Other World and sends him down Snake Way in search of King Kai, a legendary martial arts master with the ability to make Goku strong enough to help his friends battle the Saiyans.

title: Gohan's Harsh Survival Training with Dinosaurs
description: Piccolo leaves Gohan to fend for himself in the wilderness for six months so that he can become stronger and learn to take care of himself. Meanwhile, Krillin tries to break the news of Gohan's training and Goku's death to Chi-Chi. Also, Kami foresees his own demise and wonders about Piccolo's motives, and Goku continues his journey down Snake Way.

title: A Full Moon: The Secret of Gohan's Power
description: Krillin returns to the Kame house without telling Chi-Chi of Goku's death and Gohan's training with Piccolo, and Chi-Chi and the Ox King set out to find what he's hiding. Yajirobe brings a message to Krillin, telling him to find Yamcha, Tien, and Chiaotzu and to meet back at Korin Tower for special training in preparation for the Saiyans. Meanwhile, as Gohan tries to find the courage to get down from the cliff he glances at the full moon, which turns him into a giant ape, and Piccolo must find a way to stop him. Also, Goku continues down Snake Way.

title: Sorry Mr. Robot: The Tears That Disappeared in the Desert
description: Gohan is attacked by wild animals. As he attempts to escape, he falls into an underground cavern, where he finds a robot who teaches him to take care of himself. Meanwhile, Goku, who is still on Snake Way, takes a break from running to eat clouds.

title: Don't Cry! Gohan's First Battle
description: Krillin picks up Yamcha, who is playing in a baseball game. Meanwhile, Gohan gathers food and mends his wounds, and he helps a dinosaur who has been injured. Also, Goku wakes up from a nap and continues down Snake Way.

title: Saiyans: Greatest Warriors in the Universe, Awaken
description: While on their way to Earth, Vegeta and Nappa take a quick detour in an attempt to conquer the planet Arlia. Meanwhile, Gohan dines on the tail of a dinosaur, Launch runs from the police, and Goku continues down Snake Way.

title: Napping on the Path of Snake: Son Goku Falls Off!
description: Krillin and Bulma search for Tien and Chiaotzu, who are training under a waterfall, and Launch tries to convince Tien to rob banks with her. Meanwhile, Goku gets a ride from a street sweeper and Gohan continues his training. Also, Piccolo trains by lifting the Pyramids with his mind, but he accidentally causes and earthquake which affects everyone.

title: Keep Your Hands Off! Enma's Secret Fruit
description: Having fallen off Snake Way, Goku finds himself in the Land Below the Clouds. There he meets Goz and Mez, two ogres who will help him find his way back to Snake Way if he can defeat them in a series of challenges. Meanwhile, Tien and Chiaotzu climb Korin Tower; Launch meets Upa and Gora while trying to find a way to follow Tien up the tower; and Gohan runs from a tiger.

title: Sweet Seduction: The Snake Princess' Hospitality
description: Having caught up to where he was when he fell, Goku continues down Snake Way. He stops at a palace, thinking it to be where King Kai lives, but it turns out to belong to Princess Snake, who likes him so much that she won't let him leave. Meanwhile, Gohan watches Piccolo train; Krillin, Yamcha, Tien, Chiaotzu, and Yajirobe begin their training with Kami.

title: Escape from Piccolo! Gohan and the Storm
description: Gohan does his homework in a cave as he thinks about how much he misses his parents. He then makes a boat and sails across the desert, where he is chased by a giant bird. He crash lands on an island, and he befriends a tiger as he looks for a way to escape. Meanwhile, Piccolo splits himself in two and fights his doppelganger as part of his training. Also, Goku continues down Snake Way.

title: Run Gohan! Back to Mt. Paozu Where Chichi Waits
description: Having crashed his ship because of the storm, Gohan is found on the beach by a group of orphans who he stays with for awhile.

title: The Road to Victory Is Long
description: Piccolo begins heavy training with Gohan. At the Lookout, Krillin, Yamcha, Tien, and Chiaotzu grow impatient because they feel that they aren't learning anything from Kami's training, so Mr. Popo uses the time chamber to transport them back in time to planet Vegeta, where they fight two Saiyans.

title: The End of the Path of Snake
description: Piccolo is forced to fight Gohan, who turns into a giant ape when he sees the moon that is projected from Goku's Saiyan spacecraft. Meanwhile, Goku reaches the end of Snake Way and meets King Kai.

title: Catch Bubbles! The Struggle with Gravity
description: Before he can start his training, Goku must make King Kai laugh. Then, his training begins--he must catch King Kai's monkey, Bubbles. Meanwhile, Piccolo and Gohan continue to train.

title: The Legend of Saiyans: Son Goku's Roots
description: In the next phase of Goku's training, he must hit Gregory, King Kai's grasshopper, with a sledge hammer; also, King Kai tells Goku about the history of the Saiyans. Back on Earth, Piccolo continues training Gohan, and Krillin, Tien, Chiaotzu, Yamcha, and Yajirobe train at the Lookout.

title: Appear Shenlon! Saiyans Are About to Arrive
description: King Kai times Goku on catching Bubbles and Gregory, and Goku practices the Spirit Bomb technique. Goku then contacts Roshi and tells him to wish him back to life, and he begins his journey back down Snake Way. Meanwhile, as the Z Fighters finish their training, the Saiyans land on Earth.

title: That's Ridiculous! The Saiba Men Sprout from the Ground
description: Nappa destroys East City, and he and Vegeta head toward Piccolo and Gohan; the other Z Warriors also fly to where the battle is going to take place, with Krillin arriving first; Yajirobe tells a group of people about the Saiyans.

title: Yamucha Dies! The Frightening Saiba Men
description: The Z fighters and the Saiyans agree to fight a series of one on one matches, and Tien and Yamcha fight the first two saibamen while their friends watch helplessly on TV; Goku races back home as fast as he can; Yajirobe talks to a group of reporters about the battle.

title: Goodbye Tien... Chauzu's Sacrifice
description: Krillin and Piccolo finish off the saibamen, and the surviving Z Fighters fight Nappa. Meanwhile, Goku passes Princess Snake's palace as he races home.

title: Tenshihan's Final Scream! His Last Energy Beam
description: The battle with Nappa continues as Piccolo and Krillin try to ambush him while he fights Tien. Also, Kami senses that the end of his life is approaching, and Goku passes the street sweeper on Snake Way.

title: Waiting Patiently for 3 Hours: The Candy Cloud Flies
description: As everyone stops fighting to wait for Goku to arrive, Nappa goes on a rampage and engages civilians and military personnel. Also, Goku returns to Earth and rushes to the battlefield.

title: Leave It to Me: Gohan's Explosion of Anger
description: Piccolo, Krillin, and Gohan fend off Nappa as Goku makes his final approach on the flying nimbus. Meanwhile, Bulma thinks about happier times and the Ox King tries to stop Chi-Chi from joining the battle.

title: The Savagery of Saiyan! God and Piccolo Die
description: As Kami fades from existence while Piccolo dies, he tells Mr. Popo to go to the planet Namek to retrieve their dragon balls; Gohan, in a rage, fights Nappa; Fortune Teller Baba arrives at the Kame House to announce Goku's return; Goku arrives on the battlefield and fights Nappa.

title: Wow Dad! Kaio's Killer Technique
description: Goku fights Nappa.

title: A Battle Beyond Imagination: Son Goku vs. Vegeta
description: Goku fights Vegeta, and he uses the kaioken technique; Krillin and Gohan fly back to the Kame House; Launch drinks her troubles away in a bar; Vegeta causes a massive earthquake and storm while powering up.

title: Now Goku! The Last Great Effort
description: Goku and Vegeta continue to fight, and Goku uses a triple kaioken attack. Frustrated that he can't beat Goku, Vegeta attempts to destroy the world using his Galick Gun attack, and Goku gives everything he has in a desperate attempt to stop it.

title: Battle Power Tenfold! Vegeta's Great Transformation
description: Vegeta uses his energy to create artificial moonlight and turns into an ape, and Goku, after trying to fight him, realizes that his only chance for victory is to charge a spirit bomb. Meanwhile, Gohan flies back to help his dad.

title: Don't Die Dad! Gohan's Inner Power
description: Krillin, Gohan, and Yajirobe arrive to help Goku, who is being crushed by Vegeta.

title: Hit Him, Kuririn! The Energy Ball of Everyone's Prayers
description: Gohan fights Vegeta as Krillin prepares to throw the spirit bomb that he created from the last of Goku's energy. Also, Korin shows up at the Kame House, and he, Roshi, Bulma, and Chi-Chi go to help.

title: Super Saiyan, Son Goku: Performs a Mircale!
description: Yajirobe distracts Vegeta as Gohan turns into a giant ape by looking at the artificial moonlight created by Vegeta, and ape Gohan and Vegeta fight.

title: Leap Into Space! The Planet of Hope Is Piccolo's Home
description: The battle with Vegeta is over--the survivors are picked up by Roshi, Bulma, Chi-Chi, and Korin, and everybody mourns their fallen friends. Also, Krillin devises a plan to go to the planet Namek to find more dragon balls and revive their friends.

title: The Mysterious Yunzabit: Find God's Spaceship
description: Goku, Gohan, and Krillin recover in the hospital. Also, after accidentally destroying the Saiyan spaceship, Bulma goes with Mr. Popo to find another ship that Kami told him about.

title: Take off for Nameck! The Terror That Awaits
description: Bulma and her dad work on the spaceship; Gohan sneaks out of his room to train, and Chi-Chi looks for him; Goku, Gohan, and Krillin continue to recover in the hospital; Bulma recruits Gohan and Krillin to go with her to Namek.

title: Friend or Foe! Children of the Mysterious Giant Spaceship
description: Gohan, Krillin, and Bulma try to occupy themselves on their ship until they are attacked by a squadron of smaller ships. They escape, but they are captured by a command ship that is camouflaged to look like the rest of space, and they leave their own ship to investigate the inside of the command ship. Also, Goku is scolded by his doctor for training in the hospital, and Vegeta travels through space planning his revenge on Goku.

title: Really? That's the Planet of Hope, Nameck?
description: Start of the "Namek Saga". While Krillin, Gohan, and Bulma are held at gunpoint, the ship enters an asteroid belt. After they help their captors through the asteroids, the kids tell them about how the villainous Frieza killed their parents and friends and took over their planet. Meanwhile, Goku is scared to death of getting a shot at the hospital, and Vegeta arrives back at Frieza's base.

title: The Kind Aliens... A Dragonball Suddenly Appears
description: Bulma crashes the spaceship on what she believes to be Namek, and she, Krillin, and Gohan are nursed to health by two mysterious aliens. Afterward, while one of the aliens stays behind to fix the ship, the others begin searching for the dragon balls. Meanwhile, Vegeta continues his recovery, and Goku gets antsy in the hospital.

title: Planet Freeza No. 79: Vegeta Recovers
description: Gohan, Krillin, and Bulma continue looking for dragon balls. They have to retrieve one from inside a tornado, and they go to a castle where a giant lives to find the next one. Meanwhile, Goku sneaks out of the hospital to train, and Vegeta finishes his recovery.

title: All the Dragonballs Are Found: Mr. Piccolo Can Be Resurrected
description: Krillin, Gohan, and Bulma find the 6th dragon ball in an ice cave, and they must escape before the cave collapses. They also search for the final dragon ball. Meanwhile, Vegeta stews over his defeat, and he looks for Frieza. Also, Goku continues training, despite his injuries not being fully healed, and Roshi and Chi-Chi look for him.

title: A New Enemy in the Universe: Evil Lord Freeza
description: Zaacro and Raiti explain their illusion to Krillin, Gohan and Bulma. As Krillin and Gohan try to escape from the lake monsters holding them captive, the two aliens try to figure out the spaceship. Also, Krillin, Gohan, and Bulma attempt to escape the planet and continue their journey to Namek. Meanwhile, Vegeta continues to fly to Namek, and Goku tries to sneak out of the hospital again.

title: Ambitious Vegeta: I'm the Greatest Warrior!
description: Frieza and his minions gather dragon balls. Cui tracks down Vegeta, and they fight. Two of Frieza's scouts attack Gohan and Krillin and Goku does mental training in the hospital as Chi-Chi worries about Gohan.

title: Son Goku's Power Is Restored! Six Days to the Milkway
description: Gohan, Krillin, and Bulma hide in a cave when they sense the energy of Frieza and his cronies, who are looking for the 5th dragon ball. Gohan and Krillin follow them while Bulma calls Roshi and informs him of the trouble, and Roshi in turn tells Goku. Also, Yajirobe brings Goku some senzu beans, and Goku, now healed, leaves the hospital and picks up a spaceship that Dr. Brief built for him to use to get to Namek.

title: A Surprise Attack! The Target Is the Scouter
description: Gohan and Krillin watch as Frieza interrogates a group of Nameks about the six star dragon ball, and another group of Namek fighters shows up to help their friends. Meanwhile, Goku trains on his ship.

title: Gohan Is in Danger! The Death Warrior Dodoria
description: After Dodoria easily defeats the three Namek warriors, Frieza sends the elder to get the dragon ball. But when Dodoria begins to execute the remaining Nameks, Gohan has seen enough, and he intervenes. Meanwhile, Goku continues to train on his ship.

title: Explosive Dodoria and the Fearsome Shock of Vegeta!
description: Gohan, Krillin, and Dende escape from Dodoria; Dr. Brief tells Bulma that Goku is on his way; Goku takes a break from training to eat; Vegeta confronts Dodoria.

title: The Burning Escape: A Desperate Kamehameha
description: After evading Vegeta, Krillin, Gohan, and Dende return to the cave and meet with Bulma. While Goku is outside his ship fixing damage to the hull, Dr. Brief informs him that the asteroid that did the damage also knocked the ship off course, and that he is now headed directly for a star. Vegeta goes to the next village to find a dragon ball.

title: 100 Times Stronger! The Warriors Gather at Kaio
description: Vegeta fights a group of Nameks for the dragon ball that they are holding. Frieza sends Zarbon and another soldier to find the remaining dragon balls. After hearing about how Vegeta terrorized Earth, Dende decides to take Krillin to see the eldest Namek so that they can form an alliance and defeat their foes. Goku continues his training in 20 times normal gravity and Yamcha, Tien, Chiaotzu, and Piccolo arrive at King Kai's planet to train.

title: Listen Up Goku! Hands Off Freeza!
description: Goku tells King Kai and Yamcha about what has been happening on Namek, but when King Kai learns that Frieza is there, he warns Goku to stay away. Piccolo, Yamcha, Tien, and Chiaotzu must make King Kai laugh before he will train them. Krillin and Dende hide from Vegeta, who has sensed them; Vegeta fights Zarbon.

title: Goose Bump Time! Zarbon Transforms Into the Demon
description: Vegeta continues to fight Zarbon, who reveals his true form; Krillin and Dende continue flying toward the eldest Namek; Goku trains in 50 times normal gravity; Tien, Chiaotzu, and Yamcha try to catch Bubbles as Piccolo meditates.

title: Protect the Planet of Hope! Kuririn Powers Up!
description: Guru reads Krillin's mind and sees his good intentions, so he decides to help Krillin in his quest. Zarbon reports to Frieza, who grows angry with Zarbon's carelessness regarding his fight with Vegeta. Gohan goes after the dragon ball that Vegeta hid and Goku can't move after his latest training session.

title: Back from the Brink of Death, the Miracle Man: Vegeta
description: Goku continues to train on his ship, doing sit-ups. Yamcha, Tien, and Chiaotzu chase Bubbles and Gregory as part of their training while Piccolo grows frustrated with what he considers a waste of time. One of Frieza's cronies tries to revive Vegeta; Piccolo spars with Yamcha, Tien, and Chiaotzu.

title: Huge Battle Power! Freeza's Plot Crumbles
description: Vegeta steals the dragon balls from Frieza's ship, and Zarbon chases after him. Gohan finds one of the destroyed villages, where he buries the dead and finds the dragon ball that Vegeta hid. Vegeta follows Krillin, who has the last dragon ball and the gravity in Goku's spaceship increases to dangerous levels as he passes through a magnetic storm.

title: Son Goku Regains His Power in 100G
description: Goku, still in the magnetic storm, must find a way to save himself before he is crushed by the gravity; Vegeta and Zarbon fight a rematch; Gohan flies back toward his friends with the dragon ball he found.

title: Freeza's Secret Weapon! Demonic Ginyu Corps
description: Krillin reassures Bulma that Gohan has one of the dragon balls; the Ginyu Force is launched; as Yamcha, Piccolo, Tien, and Chiaotzu are training, King Kai senses the Ginyu Force; Goku keeps training at 100 times normal gravity; Gohan has a run-in with Vegeta.

title: Buruma Is in Danger! Freeza Gets the Dragonball!
description: Bulma dreams that Vegeta kills her; Vegeta ponders how to get the last dragon ball; Frieza loses his temper and fires random energy blasts; Krillin and Gohan fly toward Guru; Bulma tries to retrieve the dragon ball, which she loses in a lake; Goku fires kamehameha waves at himself to build his resistance.

title: Frontal Collism! Kamahameha and Kaio Fighting Style
description: Bulma convinces the two soldiers who captured her to go after the dragon balls for themselves, and they go to the bottom of a lake to find one; Goku trains with kaio-ken in 100 times normal gravity; Krillin and Gohan continue on their way to Guru, and Vegeta picks up their trail; Frieza gets a report that the Ginyu Force is on its way.

title: The Ultimate Battle Nears! Ginyu Special Corps Arrive
description: Vegeta catches up with Krillin and Gohan, and Krillin heads him off while Gohan visits Guru. Also, after sensing the Ginyu Force, Vegeta forges an uneasy alliance with them. Meanwhile, Goku finishes his training and relaxes.

title: Son Goku Approaches Rapidly! Break Through Freeza's Defense
description: Frieza orders the Ginyu Force to capture Vegeta, take the dragon balls, and kill Gohan and Krillin; Guldo thinks about his dislike for Vegeta; Goku prepares as his ship is on its final approach for Namek; Vegeta, Krillin, and Gohan are confronted by the Ginyu Force.

title: Awesome Magic or Trick? Mr. Gould Is Mad
description: Krillin and Gohan fight Guldo; Bulma phones in a report to Roshi; Piccolo senses that Gohan is in danger.

title: Rikuum! He's Bad! He's Strong! He's Unbelievable!
description: Vegeta fights Recoome; Frieza investigates the environmental properties of Namek.

title: Don't Die, Gohan! Son Goku Finally Arrives
description: Gohan fights Recoome; Chi-Chi worries about Gohan; Captain Ginyu delivers the dragon balls to Frieza, who tries to make his wish.

title: Son Goku, the Legendary Super Saiyan
description: After Goku revives Gohan, Krillin, and Vegeta with senzu beans and gets updated on the situation, he fights Recoome; Dr. Briefs and Chi-Chi contact Bulma.

title: The Red and Blue Lightenging Ball: Jees and Baata Attack!
description: Goku fights Jeice and Burter; Frieza flies toward Guru; Captain Ginyu holds tryouts for the Ginyu Force; Bulma grows impatient while waiting for Gohan and Krillin.

title: Finally... the Clash, Commander Ginyu Appears
description: Start of the "Captain Ginyu Saga". Goku continues to fight Jeice and Burter, and Jeice retreats to warn Captain Ginyu. Goku and Vegeta argue over the fate of the defeated Ginyu Force members, the dragon balls, and fighting Frieza and Bulma reminisces about the old days.

title: Goku's Full Power Is Awesome
description: Vegeta bails on Goku to follow Gohan and Krillin while Goku fights Captain Ginyu. Meanwhile, Bulma notices on the dragon radar that all of the dragon balls are together, and she decides to go after them.

title: The Hand of Evil Is on Senior Elder!
description: Goku charges to full power as Captain Ginyu watches. Bulma mourns the atrocities that Frieza has caused. Nail returns to Guru and Gohan and Krillin look for Bulma and her dragon radar. Guru unlocks Dende's hidden power and Frieza fights the Nameks who are guarding Guru.

title: What a Surprise! Goku Is Ginyu and Ginyu Is Goku
description: Nail lures Frieza away from Guru, and they fight; Goku fights Captain Ginyu; Bulma is chased by dinosaurs, and she scolds Gohan and Krillin when they show up.

title: Appear Super Shenlon and Grant My Wish
description: Vegeta storms Frieza's ship looking for the dragon balls. Gohan and Krillin find the dragon balls and attempt to call Shenron as Vegeta watches. Having switched bodies with Captain Ginyu, Goku rushes to find Ginyu and Jeice before they can get to Gohan and Krillin.

title: He's Not Me: Attack Your Father, Gohan
description: Gohan and Krillin fight Captain Ginyu, who is still in Goku's body; Vegeta fights Jeice; Nail continues to fight Frieza.

title: Ginyu Turned Into a Frog!
description: Captain Ginyu, back in his own body, allows Vegeta to pound on him until he is ready to attempt another body switch, but Goku has other plans; afterward, everyone prepares to fight Frieza. Meanwhile, Frieza continues to beat on Nail.

title: One Who Has All Seven Balls: Say the Right Words
description: Start of the "Frieza Saga". Goku recovers in the isolation chamber, Gohan guards the dragon balls, and Vegeta rests while they all wait on Krillin's return; Dende looks for Krillin and Gohan; Frieza finishes interrogating Nail.

title: Super Shenlon Brings God and Piccolo Back to Life
description: With Porunga summoned, Krillin, Gohan, and Dende make their wishes after Gohan consults with Piccolo; Vegeta grows angry when he wakes up and realizes what has happened; Frieza flies toward the Z Fighters.

title: The Birth of an Ultimate Warrior? Neil and Piccolo Merge
description: Frieza powers up while everyone watches; Nail tries to convince Piccolo to merge with him; the battle with Frieza begins.

title: Battle Power 1 Million: Freeza Transforms
description: Frieza talks about his history with Vegeta's father and his attempted rebellion, and he transforms into a more powerful version of himself; Bulma runs from a dinosaur stampede.

title: Is This the End? Terrifying Power Attacks Gohan
description: Frieza tortures Krillin; Yamcha becomes frustrated because he can't help his friends; Bulma despairs; in a rage, Gohan attacks Frieza.

title: A Sudden Turn of Events: The Warrior Piccolo Arrives
description: Frieza taunts Vegeta, who stands helpless as he watches Frieza stand over the defeated Gohan. Goku itches to join in the fight. Piccolo rushes to help Gohan as he thinks back on their time together and Krillin rejoins the fight to draw Frieza away from Gohan.

title: Piccolo's Confidence: I Will Defeat Freeza
description: Piccolo joins the fray and fights Frieza alone.

title: We Need You, Goku! Freeza Transforms Again!
description: The battle between Piccolo and Frieza rages on, and Frieza makes his second transformation.

title: Be Terrified! Freeza Transforms a 3rd Time!
description: In a rage, Gohan saves Piccolo from Frieza, who makes his final transformation. Meanwhile, Vegeta gets Krillin to attack him so that he can become stronger when Dende heals him.

title: Dende Dies: Bring Out the Ultimate Power!
description: After Frieza kills Dende, he fights Gohan, Piccolo, Krillin, and Vegeta.

title: Finally, Son Goku Arrives!
description: Determined to prove that he is a Super Saiyen, Vegeta gives Frieza everything he has.

title: Bitter Regret! Proud Vegeta Dies
description: Frieza continues to wail on Vegeta until Goku arrives. After Frieza recognizes Goku as the son of a former opponent, the battle is on. Also, Vegeta, near death, gives a heartfelt speech of remorse for his actions.

title: The Battle Again! I'll Defeat You Myself
description: The battle between Goku and Frieza continues after Piccolo, Gohan, and Krillin get out of their way. Also, the entire planet begins to fall apart due to the intensity of the fighting.

title: The Second Power of the Clash
description: Goku, realizing that Frieza can't sense him, formulates a plan while he is underwater, but Frieza has some tricks of his own. Meanwhile, despite everyone's best efforts, Chi-Chi is determined to go to Namek.

title: Freeza's Declaration, I'll Beat You Without Using My Hand
description: Goku and Frieza agree to keep the fight on the ground, and Frieza decides to fight without using his hands; Chi-Chi urges Dr. Briefs to fix the ship, which was broken by the Ox King; Yajirobe tries to sneak off while Puar and Oolong talk; Bulma finds Captain Ginyu, who is still in a frog's body.

title: He's Not Bragging: Son Goku Is Wonderful
description: After Goku refuses to join him, Frieza reveals that he has been using only one percent of his power. He charges to fifty percent, and he and Goku continue to fight. Meanwhile, Captain Ginyu, in Bulma's body, watches the battle as Bulma, in the frog's body, tries to tell Gohan what has happened. Back on Earth, Chi-Chi, Roshi, Yajirobe, Puar, and Oolong prepare for take-off.

title: Life or Death Decision: Kaio Style 20X Power!
description: Goku loses hope as he is thrashed by Frieza, and he must rely on his love for his friends and family to summon enough strength to rebound. Meanwhile, Gohan must find a way to return Bulma to her own body.

title: A Mega Energy Ball: His Last Ace!
description: Weakened from using kaio-ken X20, Goku takes a beating from Frieza until he receives a vision from Vegeta. Meanwhile, the Ginyu Force arrives on King Kai's planet.

title: Piccolo Stakes His Life to Attack and Aid
description: Goku gathers energy for his spirit bomb. Meanwhile, the Ginyu Force tests its powers on King Kai's planet.

title: Who Survives the Incredible Power of Energy Ball?
description: Piccolo holds off Frieza while Goku finishes forming the spirit bomb. Meanwhile, Yamcha, Tien, and Chiaotzu fight the Ginyu Force.

title: Son Goku Becomes the Legendary Super Saiyan!
description: Goku, Krillin, Piccolo, and Gohan celebrate the defeat of Frieza, but they may be celebrating too soon. Meanwhile, Yamcha, Tien, and Chiaotzu continue fighting the Ginyu Force.

title: His Rage Power! Avenge Everyone
description: Goku, now a Super Saiyan, takes out his anger on Frieza; Gohan takes Piccolo to safety; Roshi senses Goku's new power.

title: An Attack of Evil: Will Nameck Be Destroyed?
description: Frieza realizes that he can't defeat Goku, so he decides to destroy Namek; Gohan drops off Piccolo on the ship and looks for Bulma; there is a calamity at Frieza's base.

title: I'll Be the Winner! The Final Attack
description: Goku and Frieza continue to fight as the planet falls apart around them, and Frieza charges to one hundred percent power. Meanwhile, Gohan searches for Bulma.

title: Shenlon! Fly Through Space! Nameck's Destruction Nears!
description: While Goku and Frieza continue to fight, Kami and King Kai discuss how they should use the wish from the dragon balls that Mr. Popo has collected. Also, Gohan and Bulma return to the ship and try to get it working.

title: I'm Son Goku's Son! Gohan Returns to the Battle
description: Goku and Frieza continue to fight; Gohan, no longer sensing his dad's power level, decides to leave the ship and face Frieza himself; Shenron works on granting the wish.

title: His Last Wish: I Will Stay on the Planet
description: While fighting Frieza, Goku asks King Kai to change the wish to allow him to stay on the planet and finish the fight. Guru relays this to Dende, who must make the wish before Frieza notices that the dragon is back.

title: Battle to the End on a Dying Planet
description: Goku and Frieza continue to fight; Guru explains the wish to everyone who was brought to Earth; Piccolo thinks back on everything he and Goku have been through together; Vegeta explains his plan for when Goku and Frieza are dead.

title: Pitiful Freeza Cannot Stop Shaking
description: Goku and Frieza continue to fight, and Goku offers Frieza one last chance to live. Also, King Kai recaps Frieza's plan to destroy Namek. Back on Earth, the superstitious Bulma burns leaves and watches the burn pattern to determine if Goku will return from the battle.

title: Son Goku Declares Victory: Freeza Self-Destructs
description: Goku and Frieza continue to fight, with Goku trying to avoid Frieza's energy discs. Back on Earth, Vegeta thinks back on his hatred for Frieza, and he remembers the moment when he decided that he wanted to become strong enough to defeat Frieza.

title: The Defeat of Freeza
description: Lying in pieces on the ground, the defeated Frieza taunts Goku, who is walking away. Frieza then thinks back on the fight. Back on Earth, the dying Guru appoints a new leader for the Nameks.

title: Son Goku Vanishes in the Universe
description: As Goku is trying to escape from Namek, King Kai relates the action to Tien, Yamcha, and Chiaotzu. Afterward, Yamcha telepathically recounts it to Bulma through King Kai. Also, Gohan gets into a fight with Vegeta.

title: Warriors Z Come Back to Life
description: Vegeta suggests a plan to bring Goku back; Bulma invites Vegeta and the Nameks to stay with her until they can relocate; the Namekian dragon balls are used to bring Yamcha, Krillin, Tien, and Chiaotzu back and to relocate the Nameks.

title: Garlic Junior Becomes God
description: Start of the "Garlic Jr. Saga". Garlic Jr. has returned from the Dead Zone to hatch a sinister plot of revenge upon those responsible for his defeat; Gohan meets up with Krillin and Krillin's girlfriend Maron; Piccolo splits himself in four and spars with himself, and he meets with Kami; Garlic Jr. and his goons invade the Lookout; there is a reunion party at Roshi's, but Chi-Chi won't let Gohan go.

title: The Black Mist of the Horror
description: As the black water mist spreads, Garlic Jr. reveals his plan to wish his father back and to get revenge on Goku and Gohan; Gohan and Icarus run into a group of animals who have been affected by the mist; Kami tells Mr. Popo that the Serpent race that Garlic Jr. belongs to has long been an evil race that wants only destruction; Chi-Chi arrives at Roshi's house looking for Gohan, and she is offended by Maron before everyone on the island breathes the mist.

title: Heaven Turns Into a Battlefield
description: Spice reveals to Piccolo how Garlic Jr. escaped from the Dead Zone using the Makyo Star; Krillin and Gohan go to the Lookout to find the sacred water while Piccolo stays behind to fight; in outer space, Vegeta looks for Goku.

title: Face to Face! Encounter with Piccolo
description: Gohan and Krillin fight the Spice Boys; Yajirobe and Korin cook for Maron; Vegeta trains on a distant planet while looking for answers.

title: The War for Super Magic Water
description: Gohan fights Piccolo while Krillin tries to save Kami and Mr. Popo from Garlic Jr. Also, Yajirobe and Korin play cards with Maron.

title: The Life or Death Journey of God
description: Piccolo explains to Gohan what his plan was; Piccolo, Gohan, and Krillin hold off Garlic Jr., Spice, and Vinegar while Kami and Mr. Popo take the sacred water to the seven air currents of the world; Vegeta fights a group of Frieza's thugs while he searches for Goku.

title: The Mega Vigorous Battle
description: Gohan, Krillin, and Piccolo fight with Garlic Jr., Spice, and Vinegar, all three of whom are now powered up. Meanwhile, Kami and Mr. Popo carry the sacred water through the realm of the dead guardians of Earth in an attempt to reach the seven air currents, but the former guardians attempt to drain Kami's life force and keep him there forever.

title: The Ultra Holy Water Worked!! The World Awakens from Its Nightmare
description: Gohan, Krillin, and Piccolo fight Garlic, Jr. Meanwhile, Kami tries to convince the former guardians of the Earth to allow him to spread the sacred water.

title: Gohan's Brief Chance for Victory!! Hit the Makyo Planet...
description: Gohan keeps his shield up to prevent himself, Krillin, and Piccolo from being sucked into the dead zone, but Piccolo tries to convince him to lower the shield and to destroy the Makyo Star, thus destroying the source of Garlic, Jr.'s, power. Meanwhile, Kami struggles to survive as he is tortured by the former guardians of Earth.

title: You're My Guy... Krillin the 101st Proposal
description: Krillin goes shopping with Maron, and he contemplates marriage. Also, everyone is called to the Kame house for Turtle's 1000th birthday party. While there, Krillin goes deep sea diving with Gohan in search of the Mermaid's Tear, the world's largest pearl, which he plans to give to Maron.

title: That Is Earth Papa... Freeza and Father Counterattack
description: Start of the "Trunks Saga". While thinking about his decision to break up with Maron, Krillin trains hard to improve his Kamehameha wave. Chi-Chi gets Gohan a tutor named Mr. Shu, who is very strict. Bulma tells Yamcha about a dream she had of Vegeta. Vegeta returns to Earth in search of Goku and a revitalized Frieza sets his sights on Earth.

title: I Will Defeat Freeza... The Mysterious Boy Awaiting Goku
description: The Z Warriors fly to the suspected sight of the upcoming battle, Frieza and King Cold land their ship, and both sides prepare for battle.

title: Freeza Halved by a Single Blow!! Another Super Saiya-jin
description: The mysterious warrior fights Frieza and his goons. Meanwhile, the Z Warriors detect his power level and move toward the fight.

title: Heya!! It's Been a While... The Return of Son Goku
description: The mysterious Super Saiyan fights King Cold, and everyone waits on Goku's return.

title: My Dad Is Vegeta... Admissions of the Mysterious Boy
description: After testing his strength against Goku, the Super Saiyan reveals himself to be Trunks, the son of Bulma and Vegeta from the future. He warns Goku of an upcoming battle with the Androids, which will determine the fate of the entire world.

title: Goku's New Finishing Technique!?
description: Goku tells of his escape from Namek and his time spent on the planet Yardrat, and he demonstrates the Instant Transmission technique, which the people of Yardrat taught him. Also, the Z Warriors formulate a plan to fight the Androids, and they all leave to train for the upcoming battle.

title: The King of the Fighting Saiya-jin Race
description: In a desperate attempt to become a Super Saiyan, Vegeta begins a grueling training regiment. Despite suffering from injuries, he carries on as Bulma tries to convince him to slow down. Also, Yamcha watches him train and tries to keep up. Meanwhile, Goku, Gohan, and Piccolo train together.

title: License Mastery? Goku's Newest Trial
description: On her way home from the grocery, Chi-Chi is chased by a wild boar. Mad that she doesn't have a car, she makes a deal with Goku and Piccolo that she will keep doing their chores if they get their driver's licenses. Meanwhile, Vegeta keeps training hard.

title: Which Ones Are the Artificial Humans!?
description: The Z Warriors arrive at the designated spot to wait for the Androids, who appear and start their attack on the city.

title: The Cold-Blooded No. 20's Hideous Atrocities!!
description: The rest of the Z Warriors arrive to save Yamcha. Krillin takes him to safety while the others lead the Androids away from the city.

title: Caught Between Illness and Adversary
description: Goku fights Android No. 19. Meanwhile, Roshi tells Maron, who has shown up at his house looking for Krillin, about the Red Ribbon Army.

title: The Might of Vegeta!! The Blood of a Super Saiya-jin Awakens
description: Goku fights against his virus as Android No. 19 beats him up, and Vegeta steps in to save him. Meanwhile, Yajirobe plays with baby Trunks, and he drives Bulma to see the battle.

title: The Secret of Doctor Gero
description: Vegeta fights the Androids as Yamcha flies Goku home to get the antidote for his virus.

title: A Present More Terrifying Than the Future!?
description: The Z Fighters look for Android 20 as he watches them and determines who he will steal power from, and he fights Piccolo; Trunks returns; Goku gets his medicine.

title: The Search for Doctor Gero's Mysterious Lab
description: During the confusion after the explosion of Bulma's ship, Android 20 retreats to activate Androids 17 and 18; Trunks grows angry with Vegeta for not trying to save Bulma; the Z Fighters debate their next move.

title: No. 17 and No. 18 Awaken!!
description: The Z Fighters look for Dr. Gero's lab while he tries to beat them there; Gohan flies Bulma, baby Trunks, and Yajirobe home; Goku fights the virus.

title: The Ultimate Weapons to Kill Goku
description: After Androids 17 and 18 mutiny on Dr. Gero, they activate Android 16 and go after Goku. Vegeta follows the Androids while Goku continues to fight the virus as Chi-Chi cooks for him. Gohan stops so that Bulma and Yajirobe can change Trunks' diaper.

title: No. 18 Has No Blind Spot
description: Vegeta fights Android 18 while the rest of the Z Fighters fly toward the battle; Gohan continues to fly Bulma, Trunks, and Yajirobe home; Maron surfs while she stays at Roshi's house.

title: Is This the End of the Z Senshi!?
description: The rest of the Z Fighters jump in to help Vegeta, and Android 17 joins the fight; Turtle saves Maron from drowning and fights off two guys who are trying to pick her up.

title: Piccolo's Resolution!! The Last Measure in His Reserve
description: Krillin heals everyone with senzu beans. Vegeta flies off in a rage and Piccolo goes to the Lookout to speak with Kami. Krillin, Trunks, and Tien go to pick up Goku, who is still fighting the virus while Maron leaves Roshi's house. Gohan drops off Bulma, baby Trunks, and Yajirobe at Dr. Brief's house.

title: The Artificial Humans Draw Near Goku
description: Piccolo tries to convince Kami to merge with him; Tien goes to pick up Chiaotzu while Krillin and Trunks continue on to pick up Goku; the Androids hijack a truck, and they run afoul of a motorcycle gang.

title: Bulma Unveils a Mystery
description: Tien picks up Chiaotzu while the rest of the Z Fighters fly to Roshi's house as Trunks thinks about his world and how to defeat the Androids. Goku dreams about the Androids and the Androids in turn continue driving to Goku's house. Vegeta vows to ascend to an even more powerful level and Bulma reports a strange finding to Krillin and Trunks.

title: The Discovery of an Evil Egg!!
description: Start of the "Imperfect Cell Saga". Trunks, Gohan, and Bulma investigate the 2nd time machine; Goku is flown to Roshi's house; the Androids continue driving to Goku's hose; Kami, while considering Piccolo's suggestion, tells of a new disturbance that he senses.

title: Birth of a Super Namekian!!
description: The Androids battle with the police after No. 18 steals a dress; Bulma and everyone at Roshi's house, while watching the news on the television, see a crisis unfold at Gingertown; Piccolo and Kami merge.

title: The Monster Who Possesses Goku's Ki
description: Piccolo faces the creature in Gingertown; the Z Warriors sense the creature's power level, but they can't determine who or what it is, sensing him as a combination of their friends and foes; Trunks and Krillin fly to Gingertown; Android No. 16 picks up Piccolo's and the creature's power levels.

title: His Name Is Artificial Human Cell
description: The creature grabs Piccolo, draining his life force as a group of tanks enters the city and shoots at him. Also, the creature explains his origin to Piccolo. Meanwhile, Goku lies in bed recovering, and Gohan watches the TV news report on the crisis.

title: Cell Escapes Into the City!
description: Krillin and Trunks arrive to help Piccolo, but Cell leaves to recharge his energy before he takes on the Androids. Also, Piccolo explains what Cell is to the other Z Warriors.

title: The Secret of Cell's Birth! What Lies Below the Laboratory!?
description: Vegeta leaves to train by himself; Trunks and Krillin go to Gero's lab to destroy the fetus Cell from the present so that he cannot be born; Piccolo and Tien chase after the matured Cell from the future; Cell goes to Nickytown to restore his energy.

title: Go Beyond Super Saiya-jin!!
description: Cell runs amok in Nickytown; Krillin saves a young girl and her little brother and fights Cell; Piccolo and Tien arrive to help Krillin; Trunks contemplates recent events as he looks for Vegeta; the Androids drive through the woods while looking for Goku's house; the Z Warriors look for Cell; Goku awakens.

title: In the Room of Spirit and Time...
description: Goku rounds up Gohan, Trunks, and Vegeta and takes them to the Lookout, where they will train in the Time Chamber in hopes of reaching a level beyond that of a Super Saiyan. Meanwhile, the other Z Warriors look for Cell in an amusement park. Also, the Androids continue looking for Goku.

title: Piccolo vs Artificial Human No. 17
description: Piccolo fights Android 17. Meanwhile, Goku and Gohan wait for Trunks and Vegeta to finish their training in the Time Chamber. Also, Bulma works on deciphering the schematics for the Androids.

title: Cell - Prologue to Perfection
description: Piccolo continues fighting Android 17 as Cell flies toward them. Meanwhile, Bulma finishes deciphering the Android schematics, and Goku and Gohan continue waiting on Trunks and Vegeta.

title: Piccolo's Flame Burns Out!!
description: Cell fights Piccolo and Android 17. Meanwhile, Krillin goes to meet Bulma to get the remote control, and Tien goes to help Piccolo.

title: The Wordless Warrior No. 16 Takes Action!!
description: Goku, Gohan, and Mr. Popo all express anger and sadness at the defeat of Piccolo; Bulma flies toward the Z Warriors with the remote control; Cell fights Androids 17 and 16.

title: The Transforming Cell Is a Super Gourmet
description: Android 16 and Tien fight Cell in an attempt to protect Androids 17 and 18.

title: Tomorrow I Am Going to Pulverize You!!
description: Start of the "Perfect Cell Saga". Tien holds off Cell as Androids 16 and 18 escape, and Yamcha, Chiaotzu, Goku, and Gohan all debate helping him. Meanwhile, Krillin gets the remote from Bulma.

title: A Reborn Vegeta, Father and Son, Sally Forth
description: After Bulma brings them new Saiyan armor, Vegeta and Trunks go after Cell as Goku and Gohan prepare to enter the Time Chamber. Meanwhile, Cell looks for the Androids.

title: The Super Power of a Radiant Vegeta
description: Vegeta challenges Cell, who is still looking for the Androids. Meanwhile, Goku gives Gohan a pep talk in the Time Chamber.

title: I Am Super Vegeta!!
description: Vegeta fights Cell while Trunks recalls his experiences in the Time Chamber. Meanwhile, Goku trains Gohan in the Chamber.

title: A Challenge to Cell's Perfect Form
description: Vegeta continues his fight with Cell. In the Time Chamber, Goku trains his Kamehameha Wave, and Gohan convinces Goku to let him train harder after having a dream of almost becoming a Super Saiyan.

title: Krillin's Handiwork in Destroying No. 18
description: Cell tries to convince Vegeta to allow him to absorb Android 18 in order to reach his perfect form, thus giving Vegeta the challenge he desires. Meanwhile, Krillin tries to get close enough to the Androids to use the remote and destroy 18, but his feelings for her get in the way.

title: Cell, a Spectacular Evolution Toward His Perfect Form
description: Having convinced Vegeta to step aside, Cell goes after Android 18. Trunks tries to stop Cell, but Vegeta, wanting Cell to reach his perfect form, fends Trunks off.

title: Birth of the God of Destruction Named Cell
description: Cell completes his transformation. In the Time Chamber, Gohan pushes Goku to train him harder.

title: An Absolutely Perfect Terror Closes In!!
description: Trunks revives Krillin while Vegeta fights Cell. In the Time Chamber, Goku and Gohan train together as Super Saiyans.

title: Super Saiya-jin!! Trunks Summons a Storm
description: Vegeta makes a final attempt to defeat Cell as Trunks waits for the right time to step in.

title: Trunks' Fury, Which Scorches Even the Heavens
description: Trunks powers up and fights Cell while Krillin takes Vegeta to safety. In the Time Chamber, Goku and Gohan continue to train.

title: Trunks, the Man Who Lived Through Hell
description: Trunks reflects on his past and why he is in this dimension, and Cell does the same.

title: Cell, a Shocking Bombshell Declaration
description: Trunks continues to fight Cell while Krillin revives Vegeta with a senzu bean. In the Time Chamber, Goku discovers a weakness in the new form that he and Trunks have mastered.

title: The Mystery of the New Tenkaichi Budoukai
description: Start of the "Cell Games Saga". Trunks explains Cell's tournament to the Z Fighters; Krillin takes Android 16 to Bulma so that she can repair him; Goku and Gohan continue to train in the Time Chamber; Roshi recaps the events of the previous World Martial Arts Tournaments; Cell builds an arena for his tournament.

title: Call for Death with an Exclusive Live Broadcast
description: Dr. Brief takes a look at Android 16; Yamcha and Krillin decide to train; Gohan has a bad dream about Cell; Cell announces his tournament on TV.

title: Goku and Gohan... The Hero Father and Son's Ultimate Level-Up
description: Goku and Gohan emerge from the Time Chamber, and Goku uses his instant transmission to pay a visit to Cell in order to see how powerful he is in his perfect form; meanwhile, people are fleeing from the cities and Dr. Brief and Bulma run tests on Android 16.

title: Son Goku's Composure!? Just Rest and Wait for the Cell Games
description: Goku asks Korin to compare his strength to Cell's. He and Gohan then pick up Chi-Chi from Roshi's, and they spend the rest of the day relaxing and fishing with Krillin. Meanwhile, Cell trains in space.

title: The Girl, the Lie, and Gohan's Decision
description: While on an errand for his mom, Gohan stops in Chazke Village. He finds that Mr. Bourbon, the tycoon who runs the city, has built a shelter to protect the town from Cell, and that he manipulates the townspeople into doing what he wants. To make matters worse, he has hired General Tao as his right hand man. Along with an elderly shopkeeper named Lao and Lao's granddaughter Lime, Gohan tries to convince the people of Bourbon's and Tao's treachery, and that the shelter won't protect them from Cell.

title: The Hidden Strength!! When Gohan Was a Baby
description: Chi-Chi kicks Goku out of the house so that she can prepare for Gohan's birthday party. She looks through a photo album and thinks back on how she and Goku chose Gohan's name. Meanwhile, Goku fishes with Krillin, and he recalls a time when he lost control of Gohan's stroller.

title: Find a New Kami-sama!!
description: Piccolo emerges from the Time Chamber, and Vegeta enters; Bulma works on Android 16; Goku, Gohan, Krillin, and Chi-Chi have a picnic; the military attacks Cell; Goku sets out to find a new guardian for Earth.

title: Dende's New Occupation!! The Dragonballs Revived
description: Goku takes Dende to the Lookout, then takes Gohan and Krillin to see him. At the Lookout, Dende recreates the dragon balls, and Goku goes after them. Meanwhile, Mr. Hercule Satan, the champion of the most recent World Martial Arts Tournament, announces his entry into the Cell Games.

title: Goku's Perplexing Problem!?
description: As Goku looks for the dragon balls, he runs into General Tao, who is collecting the dragon balls for a gangster. Meanwhile, Vegeta emerges from the Time Chamber, and Hercule Satan plays to a crowd.

title: The Opening to the Decisive Battle
description: The Z Fighters fly to the Cell Games, and Hercule Satan taunts Cell.

title: The Great Satan Army Arrives
description: Two of Hercule Satan's students, Piroshki and Caroni, arrive, and all three fight Cell.

title: The Super-Tense Cell Game
description: The fight between Goku and Cell begins.

title: Cell's Huge Kamehameha
description: After powering up, Goku and Cell continue to fight. Cell uses Tien's Multi-Form Technique, Frieza's energy disk, and the Kamehameha Wave.

title: Goku, a Secret Turnabout Plan
description: Goku and Cell speed up their fighting, and Cell destroys the arena. Meanwhile, Dende watches from the Lookout.

title: The End of the Desperate Struggle!! Goku Surrenders!?
description: Cell regenerates and continues to fight as Goku's energy dwindles.

title: Someone Who Will Succeed the Strongest... His Name Is Gohan
description: Goku bows out, and Gohan steps in to fight Cell.

title: Get Mad, Gohan!! Release the Sleeping Power Within
description: Gohan fights Cell, and he tells Cell about the dramatic increase in his power when he is angered.

title: The Cell Juniors Attack
description: Cell tries to anger Gohan in order to see his true power, and Android 16 joins the fight.

title: The Tragedy of No. 16!! Super Gohan's Anger Explodes
description: The Cell Juniors attack the Z Fighters.

title: The Cell Juniors Destroyed
description: Having reached a higher power level through his anger, Gohan single-handedly takes on the Cell Juniors.

title: Cell Is KO!! Taken Down with 2 Punches
description: Gohan fights Cell, who charges to his full power, and Trunks revives the other Z Fighters with senzu beans.

title: Cell's Disaster!! The Destruction of His Perfect Body
description: Gohan walks through Cell's best attacks like they are nothing, so Cell tries to destroy the Earth.

title: Bye-Bye Everyone! Goku's Last Shunkan Idou
description: Having been reverted to his imperfect form after Gohan's last attack, Cell, in a last ditch effort, again tries to destroy the Earth, and Goku must stop him.

title: A Nightmare Reborn!!
description: Cell explains how he survived the blast, and Vegeta, filled with rage over Cell's attack on Trunks, goes ballistic and fights Cell.

title: From Goku to Gohan... A Father's Spirit Passed Down
description: Cell explains how he traveled to this time-line and how he reached his perfect form, and Goku telepathically gives Gohan an inspirational speech. Meanwhile, Fortune Teller Baba lets Chi-Chi watch the battle through her crystal ball.

title: The Fight Is Over... Thank You Son Goku
description: Gohan and Cell match energy waves, and each one struggles for control. Also, the other Z Fighters help Gohan.

title: I Will Carry on in the Next World!! Farewell with a Smile
description: Krillin, Yamcha, Tien, and Piccolo take Android 18, Gohan, and Trunks to the Lookout so that Dende can heal them, and they all summon the eternal dragon to undo the damage that Cell caused. Vegeta, angered by the death of Goku and embarrassed by his inferiority to Gohan and Cell, vows to never fight again. Hercule Satan takes the credit for Cell's defeat.

title: A New Day Will Come... Father! I'll Hang in There
description: After Krillin uses the second wish to remove the bomb from inside Android 18, the Z Fighters all go their separate ways--Gohan goes home to tell Chi-Chi about Goku's death, and he spends time with the Ox King. Trunks goes back to his own time; and Piccolo remains at the Lookout. Meanwhile, Hercule Satan displays his martial arts skills on TV, and Goku and King Kai decide to build a house in Other World.

title: End It All Again!! I Will Protect the Future
description: Back in his own time, Trunks fights the Androids and Cell. Meanwhile, Goku and King Kai decide to travel across Other World.

title: The Awesome Guy from the Next World
description: Start of the "Great Saiyaman Saga". After King Kai explains to Goku that there are actually four Kais and one Grand Kai, they go to visit the Grand Kai's planet. There, Kai has words with West Kai, Goku meets a fighter named Pikkon, and Goku and Pikkon go to hell to stop Cell and Frieza, who are running amok.

title: I'm the Greatest in the Next World! The Great Assembly of Successive Generation's Hero's
description: Goku meets the other warriors from the North quadrant, and the other Kais give King Kai grief for being dead. The Kais propose a tournament to be held amongst the warriors on the planet, and Goku races East Kai to determine if he deserves to be included.

title: Wild Enthusiasm on Dai Kaio's Planet!! Goku Stirs a Whirlwind
description: The quarter-finals of the Other World Tournament begin: Torbie faces Tapkar, Froug faces Maraikoh, Arqua faces Goku, and Pikkon faces Olibu.

title: A Blazing Decision!! Will It Be Goku or Paikuhan!?
description: The semi-finals of the Other World Tournament begin: Goku faces Maraikoh, and Pikkon faces Torbie. Also, the finals begin.

title: The Victory Escapes!! A Great Deciding Kamehameha
description: Goku faces Pikkon in the finals of the Other World Tournament.

title: It's Been 7 Years Since That Event! From Now on I'm a High School Student
description: After foiling a bank robbery, Gohan tries to fit in and make friends on his first day of high school, all while trying to hide his powers from everyone.

title: The Great Saiyaman Appears
description: Gohan gets Bulma to make a costume for him, and he takes it for a spin. While patrolling, he prevents a crazy driver from causing too much damage, and he stops a bus hijacking with Videl.

title: Gohan's Mixed-Up First Date!?
description: When Gohan's classmate Angela learns his big secret, she blackmails him into going on a date. As Saiyaman, Gohan helps put out a building fire with Videl.

title: Gohan, You Must Move Quick! Rescue Videl!!
description: Videl follows Saiyaman in an attempt to learn his identity. Also, the Red Shark Gang holds the mayor hostage, and Gohan (as Saiyaman) and Videl must rescue him.

title: The Culprit Is the Saiyaman!?
description: Gohan steals a baby dinosaur from the circus in an attempt to return him to his parents before they go on a rampage, and he is chased by Videl and the police.

title: Goku's Also Resurrected!? He's Coming to the Tenkaichi Budoukai!!
description: Gohan gets Bulma to make him a new costume for the World Martial Arts Tournament, and Vegeta announces his entry into the tournament. Also, Goku announces that he will be allowed to come back to Earth for one day to compete, and Gohan, while on the way to tell his friends of Goku's return, stumbles onto the set of a Great Saiyaman movie.

title: Gohan Is Surprised Too! Goten's Explosive Power
description: The Z Fighters train for the upcoming World Martial Arts Tournament. While training, Gohan finds out some surprising information regarding Goten.

title: Videl Learns How to Use Bukujutsu
description: Gohan teaches Goten and Videl to fly; Goku trains in Other World as King Kai challenges South Kai to enter his new fighter in the World Martial Arts Tournament with Goku; Vegeta and Trunks train in the gravity chamber.

title: Welcome Back Goku! The Whole Z Team Is Gathered!!
description: The Z Fighters finish their training and go to the World Martial Arts Tournament.

title: You're in Danger Saiyaman! Guard Yourself Against Camera Attacks!?
description: After failing to woo Videl, Sharpener tries to discover the identity of Saiyaman as all of the fighters attempt to earn a spot in the World Martial Arts Tournament by scoring highly on a machine that measures striking power.

title: No Small Matter!! Little Trunks
description: The start of the "World Tournament Saga". The Junior World Martial Arts Tournament begins, and a filmed reenactment of the Cell Games, with Mr. Satan as the hero, is played on a giant TV screen.

title: It's My Turn!! Goten, an Anxious First Fight
description: Trunks and Goten rapidly advance to the finals of the Junior World Martial Arts Tournament, and the finals begin.

title: The Junior Champion Is Decided!!
description: Trunks and Goten continue fighting in the finals of the Junior World Martial Arts Tournament.

title: Now What, Satan!? The Greatest Pinch in History
description: Having won the Junior World Martial Arts Tournament, Trunks gets to fight Mr. Satan in an exhibition match. Also, as the Z Fighters prepare for their own matches, they meet two other mysterious fighters.

title: Event Match-ups Decided!! Let's Hurry and Hold the First Round
description: Trunks and Goten figure out a way to compete in the adult portion of the World Martial Arts Tournament, and all of the qualified fighters draw to see who will fight whom in the first round.

title: What's the Matter Piccolo!! An Unheard-of No-Fight Forfeit
description: The first round of the World Martial Arts Tournament begins, with Krillin facing Pintar and Piccolo facing Shin.

title: The Mystery of Spopovich
description: The first round of the World Martial Arts Tournament continues with Videl fighting Spopovitch. Also, Shin's true identity is revealed to Piccolo.

title: A Tragic Videl!! Are You Coming Out, Angry Super Gohan
description: Videl and Spopovitch continue their fight in the first round of the World Martial Arts Tournament.

title: Exposed!! The Saiyaman Is Son Gohan
description: Goku returns from Korin's Tower with some senzu beans, and Gohan takes them to Videl; Mr. Satan stays with Videl in the hospital; Spopovitch and Yamu monitor the power levels of the other fighters in the tournament; Gohan and Kibito get in the ring.

title: Gohan's Power Is Stolen
description: After Gohan goes Super Saiyan, Spopovitch and Yamu drain his energy and fly away. Afterward, the Z Warriors follow them to see where they're going, and the mystery behind the recent events is explained to them by Shin and Kibito.

title: The Man Behind the Curtains Appears!! The Evil Mage Babidi
description: Start of the "Babidi Saga". The Z Fighters follow Spopovitch and Yamu to Babidi, and, while observing their meeting, they see some of Babidi's other henchmen. Back at the tournament, the crowd grows restless while waiting for the next fight.

title: A Challenge from the Demon Realm
description: After Dabura neutralizes Kibito, Krillin, and Piccolo, the other Z Fighters follow him into Babidi's spaceship.

title: Vegeta's Breakthrough Fist Strike of Fury
description: Vegeta fights Pui Pui in Stage One of Babidi's ship. Back at the tournament, Goten and Trunks look for a place to relax.

title: Goku's Power Wide Open!! Blow Away Yakon
description: Goku fights Yakon in Stage Two of Babidi's ship. Back at the tournament, Trunks and Goten eat their way into trouble.

title: Satan vs 3 Super Warriors!?
description: The Z Warriors wait on the Stage Three opponent, Dabura, as he meditates to gain strength. Back at the tournament, the five remaining fighters--Killa, Jewel, Mr. Satan, Mighty Mask, and Android 18--begin a battle royale to determine the winner of the tournament.

title: Such Strong Kids!! No. 18's Close Fight!?
description: The Z Fighters continue to wait on Dabura, who is still meditating. Back at the tournament, Android 18 fights Goten and Trunks (disguised as Mighty Mask) in the battle royale, as Mr. Satan sits back and watches.

title: Confrontation with the Demon King! It's Your Turn Gohan!!
description: Android 18 fights Mr. Satan in the World Martial Arts Tournament; after seeing each other while flying, Videl tells Trunks and Goten where their fathers are; the fight between Gohan and Dabura begins.

title: A Wicked Heart Discovered!! Dabura's Great Idea
description: Gohan's fight with Dabura continues. During the fight, Dabura notices that Vegeta has a dark side.

title: Vegeta, Prince of Destruction, Revived!!
description: Babidi takes over Vegeta's mind, and he transports the Z Fighters back to the tournament.

title: The Clash of Goku vs Vegeta
description: Goku attempts to talk Vegeta into breaking Babidi's control over him while Babidi tries to convince Vegeta to kill the Supreme Kai.

title: Just You Wait, Babidi!! Your Aspirations Will Not Be Allowed
description: Goku fights Vegeta. Also, Gohan and the Supreme Kai make it to the inner sanctum of Babidi's ship.

title: The Seal Is Broken! Out Comes the Vicious Majin Buu!!
description: Goku and Vegeta continue to fight, giving Majin Buu the energy he needs to hatch.

title: I Won't Allow the Revival!! A Kamehameha of Resistance
description: Gohan tries to destroy Majin Buu's egg before it hatches; Goku and Vegeta continue to fight; Mr. Satan reassures the crowd at the tournament; Trunks and Goten try to find the battle.

title: A Straight Line to Despair!? The Grief of Kaioshin
description: Majin Buu easily pummels Dabura; Goku tries to convince Vegeta to stop fighting with him so that they can concentrate on Majin Buu; Mr. Satan reflects on his experiences with the Z Fighters, and he is accosted by reporters; Babidi commands Majin Buu to kill Gohan and the Supreme Kai.

title: Death's Dread Draws Near Gohan
description: Gohan and the Supreme Kai fight Majin Buu; Mr. Satan attempts to fly; Dabura, realizing how dangerous Majin Buu is, tries to convince Babidi to reseal him before it's too late; Trunks and Goten reach the battle site.

title: Gonna Eat'cha!! A Hungry Majin's Supernatural Power
description: Dabura and Vegeta fight Majin Buu.

title: A Warrior's Resolution!! I Will Dispose of the Majin
description: Vegeta continues to fight Majin Buu.

title: For Those Whom He Loves... Vegeta Perishes!!
description: After being saved by the intervention of Trunks and Goten, Vegeta decides to put an end to Majin Buu, even if it costs him his life. Also, Piccolo fights with Babidi.

title: The Nightmare Revisited! Majin Buu Has Survived
description: In the aftermath of the battle with Majin Buu, the remaining Z Fighters and their friends look for survivors.

title: The Struggle of Videl and the Others! Find the Dragonballs
description: Having already found the first six dragon balls, Yamcha, Roshi, Android 18, Bulma, Chi-Chi, and Videl search for the last one. Piccolo and Krillin take Trunks and Goten to the Lookout to recover, and they talk with Dende about the current situation. Babidi and Majin Buu run amok and Goku wakes up.

title: Enormous Hope!! A New Finishing Technique for the Little Squirts
description: Goku, Piccolo, Krillin, Mr. Popo, and Dende discuss strategy for defeating Majin Buu, and Goku explains the Fusion Technique, which he learned in Other World; Majin Buu causes trouble at an amusement park; Bulma uses the dragon balls to call upon Shenron, the eternal dragon.

title: Goten and Trunks! The World's Most Wanted
description: Kibito looks for Gohan and the Supreme Kai; Majin Buu causes trouble at a bakery; Goku tells those who do not know of Gohan and Vegeta's fates; Babidi telepathically communicates his plans and desires to everyone on Earth.

title: Gohan Revived! Kaioshin's Secret Weapon!?
description: Babidi and Majin Buu continue their reign of terror as they fish for the whereabouts of Trunks, Goten, and Piccolo. Trunks and Goten explore the Lookout. Gohan arrives on the Planet of the Kais with Kibito and the Supreme Kai, and he is told of the Z Sword.

title: The Legendary Z Sword
description: Videl refuses to believe that Gohan is dead; Gohan removes the Z Sword and tries to wield it; Goku begins preparing Trunks and Goten for the Fusion Technique; Majin Buu destroys another city; Mr. Satan tries a new method of learning to fly, and his fans beg him to defeat Majin Buu.

title: West City Is Targeted! Stop, Majin Buu!!
description: Trunks and Goten practice raising their power to the same level for the Fusion Technique; Mr. Satan reassures the crowd; Babidi discovers that Trunks lives at Capsule Corporation, so Goku heads off Babidi and Majin Buu while Trunks races home.

title: An Astounding, Great Transformation!! Super Saiya-jin 3
description: After explaining the different levels of a Saiyan to Babidi and Majin Buu, Goku transforms into Super Saiyan 3 and fights Majin Buu; at Capsule Corporation, Trunks looks for the dragon radar.

title: Bye-Bye, Babidi!! Majin Buu Rebels
description: Goku continues his battle with Majin Buu as Trunks continues searching Capsule Corporation for the dragon radar. Back on the Planet of the Kais, Gohan continues to train with the Z Sword.

title: Absurdly Awful Looking!? The Special Training Transformation Pose
description: Free from Babidi's control, Majin Buu causes even more destruction. Meanwhile, Gohan continues training with the Z Sword, and Goku teaches Trunks and Goten the Fusion Dance.

title: See You Later Everybody!! Goku Returns to the Other World
description: Trunks and Goten continue to practice the Fusion Dance. Meanwhile, Majin Buu, after terrorizing a farm, builds a house and spends the day there.

title: Where Is Gohan!? Training in the Kaioshin Realm
description: Back in Other World, Goku finds Gohan on the Planet of the Kais and tells him what's been happening on Earth; Piccolo takes over the duty of training Trunks and Goten for the Fusion; Majin Buu befriends a blind boy.

title: The Z Sword Is Broken
description: After Gohan accidentally breaks the Z Sword while testing its strength, an old Kai who was trapped inside the sword is released, and he promises to awaken Gohan's sleeping powers. Meanwhile, Trunks and Goten continue practicing the Fusion Dance.

title: Birth of a Superhuman Warrior!! His Name Is Gotenks
description: After several mess ups, Trunks and Goten finally fuse correctly, and the new entity, Gotenks, goes after Majin Buu, who is busy destroying ships. Meanwhile, Old Kai continues the ceremony to unlock Gohan's sleeping powers.

title: The Final Weapon Is Engaged!? Satan Will Save the Earth
description: Having been defeated easily by Majin Buu in their first battle, Trunks and Goten practice the Fusion Technique with renewed vigor; Mr. Satan emerges from his training facility and goes to Majin Buu's house; Old Kai finishes his ceremony to awaken Gohan's sleeping powers.

title: Majin Buu's Good Boy Declaration
description: Gohan and Old Kai meditate; Trunks and Goten fuse while they are both Super Saiyans; two thugs run amok, killing everyone they see; Majin Buu befriends a puppy.

title: Run Away, Satan!! An Angry Majin Buu Emerges
description: Start of the "Fusion Saga". In a rage, Mr. Satan fights the two thugs. Majin Buu heals the puppy, rebuilds his house, and relaxes with Mr. Satan. Gohan grows impatient with waiting, and he tells Old Kai about Bulma. One of the thugs comes back to cause trouble for Majin Buu and Piccolo scolds Trunks and Goten for being gone for too long.

title: A Good and Evil Buu Buu Confrontation
description: Majin Buu fights Bad Buu; Trunks and Goten rest.

title: Earth's Humanity Exterminated
description: As Majin Buu waits on Gotenks, he goes about killing the rest of Earth's population; Krillin tries to sneak Trunks and Goten into the time chamber; Gohan grows increasingly impatient with waiting.

title: The Special Training Is a Success!! You're Finished Now, Majin Buu
description: Trunks and Goten train in the time chamber as Majin Buu waits and Piccolo stalls.

title: A Wide-Open Super Gotenks
description: Gotenks starts fast as he fights Majin Buu, using a variety of new techniques.

title: Buu Successfully Eliminated with Ghosts!?
description: Gotenks uses the Super Ghost Kamikaze Attack against Majin Buu; Goku can't sense Gotenks' or Majin Buu's energy, and he realizes that they're fighting in the time chamber; Mr. Satan and Bee wander the desert and think about their time with Majin Buu.

title: Escape from Another Dimension!! Super Gotenks 3
description: Majin Buu escapes the time chamber. As Piccolo and Gotenks try to find a way out, Majin Buu terrorizes the Lookout, and Goku, Kibito, and the Supreme Kai look on helplessly through their crystal ball.

title: Buu Buu Volleyball
description: Super Saiyan 3 Gotenks fights Majin Buu. Also, Mr. Satan and Bee find a city.

title: A Reborn Gohan Returns to Earth
description: As his fusion runs out, Gotenks continues fighting against Majin Buu. Also, Gohan finishes his training.

title: Buu Overwhelmed!! Gohan's Miracle Power
description: Goten and Trunks try to sneak up on Majin Buu, who has fallen asleep. Also, Gohan returns to Earth and fights Majin Buu.

title: Majin Buu's Great Explosion
description: As Majin Buu continues to fight Gohan, he realizes that he can't win, so he self-destructs, hoping to take Gohan with him. Afterward, Gohan, Piccolo, Goten, and Trunks search for Dende, and they find Mr. Satan and Bee wandering in the desert.

title: Buu's Worst Foul!! Gotenks Is Absorbed!?
description: Majin Buu absorbs Gotenks and Piccolo, and he continues to fight Gohan.

title: For the Sake of the Entire Universe... Return to Life, Son Goku
description: Majin Buu pummels Gohan as Goku and Vegeta prepare to return to Earth.

title: Will the Super Combination with Gohan Come About
description: Old Kai explains to Goku how the earring fusion works. Also, Tien and Goku show up to help Gohan, who is still getting pounded by Majin Buu.

title: Merged!! Vegeta's Pride and Goku's Rage
description: Vegeta returns to Earth, and he and Goku fight Majin Buu. Also, Goku tries to convince Vegeta to fuse with him.

title: Vegetto Surpasses the Ultimate
description: Vegito, the fusion between Goku and Vegeta, fights Majin Buu; Dende and Mr. Satan look for the battle; in Other World, Videl, Chi-Chi, Bulma, and Dabura look for Gohan.

title: A Fissure Between Dimensions!! Has Buu Snapped!?
description: Super Saiyan Vegito fights Majin Buu; Krillin gets the tour of the Grand Kai's planet as Yamcha trains.

title: The Ace Up Buu's Sleeve!! You Become a Hard Candy
description: Vegito continues fighting Majin Buu, who is getting frustrated and is using the special attacks of the people he has absorbed. In Other World, Videl tries to convince everyone that Gohan is still alive.

title: Vegetto Is Absorbed
description: Vegito is turned into candy by Majin Buu, but he continues to fight; King Kai considers sending Krillin and Yamcha back to Earth to help in the battle; King Yemma tells Fortune Teller Baba the story of how he convinced Vegeta to help.

title: What Is There Inside Buu's Belly!?
description: Goku and Vegeta, separated inside Majin Buu's body, try to find a way out. Meanwhile, Majin Buu, thrilled with himself for having absorbed Vegito, goes on a destructive rampage.

title: Goku and Gohan's Father-Son Confrontation
description: Goku and Vegeta befriend a family of worms living inside Majin Buu. They continue searching for Trunks, Goten, Gohan, and Piccolo, but instead they find versions of them that Majin Buu has created in his mind, and they must fight them. Meanwhile, Majin Buu eats everything he can find.

title: A Majin's Secret!! 2 More Buu's Inside of Buu
description: Goku and Vegeta try to rescue their friends from Majin Buu's mind, and they find the good Buu trapped their as well. Also, Majin Buu enters his own mind and fights Goku and Vegeta.

title: Where Is the Exit!? Escape from a Collapsing Buu
description: Start of the "Kid Buu Saga". Goku and Vegeta disconnect the good Buu from Majin Buu's mind, retrieve the pods containing their friends, and attempt to escape as Majin Buu's body begins to change.

title: Earth Disappears!! Buu's Reverse-Transformation of Evil
description: Kibito Kai tells the story of how Bibidi created Majin Buu, and his battle with the Kais. Also, Majin Buu attempts to destroy Earth.

title: Buu's Assault!! A Conclusion in the Kaioshin Realm
description: Mr. Satan tries to convince himself that everything that has happened is just a dream; Majin Buu destroys lots of planets while looking for Goku and Vegeta, who are trying to form a plan revolving around the use of the dragon balls.

title: Seize the Future!! A Decisive Battle with the Universe at Stake
description: Goku fights Majin Buu.

title: Vegeta Takes Off His Hat!! Goku, You Are No. 1
description: Goku, now at Super Saiyan 3, and Vegeta take turns fighting Majin Buu, and Vegeta admires Goku's abilities.

title: Pull Through, Vegeta!! 1 Life-Threatening Minute
description: Super Saiyan 3 Goku continues to fight Majin Buu, who taunts him. Also, Vegeta holds Majin Buu off so that Goku can power up.

title: Don't You Pick on Satan!! The Original Buu Is Revived
description: Vegeta continues holding off Majin Buu as Goku powers up, and Mr. Satan lends a hand. Also, Kibito Kai and Dende consider helping.

title: Vegeta's Secret Plan!! Porunga and the 2 Wishes
description: Vegeta tells Dende, Kibito Kai, and Old Kai to go to New Namek so that they can use their dragon balls to restore Earth and its population. Meanwhile, good Majin Buu fights evil Majin Buu.

title: A Last Hope!! We'll Make a Huge Genki-dama
description: Vegeta calls upon Earth's population to give up their energy to Goku, who begins charging his Spirit Bomb. Meanwhile, good Majin Buu continues to fight evil Majin Buu. Also, the people of Earth celebrate their new lives.

title: The Genki-dama from Everyone Is Finished
description: Good Majin Buu and Vegeta hold off evil Majin Buu as Goku and Mr. Satan beg the people of Earth for their help.

title: Son Goku Is Strongest After All!! Majin Buu Is Eliminated
description: After good Majin Buu and Mr. Satan save Vegeta, Goku releases his Spirit Bomb in a final attempt to destroy evil Majin Buu.

title: Peace Returns!! Majin Buu, Champion of Justice!?
description: The Z Fighters and the people of Earth celebrate after the defeat of Majin Buu. Also, Dende heals good Majin Buu, who attempts to adjust to his new life on Earth.

title: You're Late, Goku! Everyone Party!!
description: The Z Fighters gather for a party at Bulma's house while Goku protects a bird's egg.

title: Grandpa Goku! I Am Pan!!
description: It is ten years after the defeat of Majin Buu. Trunks shows up at Goku's house, where he talks to Chi-Chi, Gohan, and Videl. He then goes out to the country to meet Goku and Goten, who are training. Vegeta and Bulma also arrive, and Goku tells everyone of his plans to enter the World Martial Arts Tournament because he thinks there will be a serious challenger this year. Also, Pan, the daughter of Gohan and Videl, arrives and announces her plan to enter the tournament as well. Later, everyone arrives at the tournament and gets settled.

title: I Am Uub! Now 10 Years Old, the Former Majin!?
description: The competitors who have made it past the preliminary round of the World Martial Arts Tournament draw numbers to determine who will fight whom in the next round, and the fights begin as Pan faces Wild Tiger and Goku faces Uub.

title: Even Stronger!! Goku's Dream Is Super-Huge
description: Goku continues to fight Uub, the reincarnation of Majin Buu, at the World Martial Arts Tournament.
